<br>
DW spec just increases the chance to attack with both hands, it has no affect on the amount of damage either weapon can do.<br>
<br>
So, weapon spec does affect how much damage your unstyled offhand will do.  This would be fairly easy to test for yourself on Pendragon.<br>
<br>
